node.text: “I think I derive my confidence from my mother. She would always say that, you know, ‘You walk into a room, it won’t matter who’s staring at you, why they’re staring at you. If you’re confident, it just enhances your true beauty.’” Thank you so much for sharing your story, Neha (@nehapanjwani). Your confidence and positivity are inspiring, and we 100% agree you can conquer the world ❤️
